1.0.0.name: wordpress/geo-redirector
1.0.0.description: This is a WordPress plugin , this plugin will allow you to redirect your URLs according to the visitors geographical location. And you can manage redirect the visitor given radios inside or outside.This plugin was developed by AnushkaKR.
